295
00:15:25,458 --> 00:15:27,833
But that won't work if
you go tattling on me.

296
00:15:27,916 --> 00:15:30,166
So I'll have to make sure
you don't leave here alive!

297
00:15:30,250 --> 00:15:31,833
[FEMALE BUGGYS shout]

298
00:15:31,916 --> 00:15:34,166
Pyuko. Go hide, this isn't safe!

299
00:15:34,250 --> 00:15:36,875
