Pyuko will hide.

300
00:15:36,958 --> 00:15:39,000
[LAWREY] Now, girls!
I want them dead!

301
00:15:39,083 --> 00:15:39,916
[FEMALE BUGGYS houts]

302
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:41,500
[TAMOTSU, MATOME shout]

303
00:15:42,916 --> 00:15:47,875
[FEMALE BUGGYS shout]

304
00:15:50,291 --> 00:15:52,958
[LAWREY growls]

305
00:15:53,041 --> 00:15:55,125
[LAWREY]
Then I'll destroy you myself!

306
00:15:55,208 --> 00:15:59,291
[shouts]

307
00:15:59,375 --> 00:16:01,833
[LAWREY gasps]
How did you do that?

308
00:16:01,916 --> 00:16:05,875
Those spanx and control top
were so hard to put on!

309
00:16:05,958 --> 00:16:08,458
[LAWREY growls]
It can't end like this!

310
00:16:10,041 --> 00:16:13,000
[laughs]

311
00:16:13,625 --> 00:16:15,041
What are you doing?

312
00:16:15,125 --> 00:16:17,500
[LAWREY] Prepare to suffer the
great curse of the sheep!

313
00:16:17,583 --> 00:16:20,250
[laughs]

314
00:16:21,916 --> 00:16:23,916
[TAMOTSU]
Um, what?

315
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:26,041
Pyuko receiving
video transmission

316
00:16:26,125 --> 00:16:28,041
