317
00:16:28,125 --> 00:16:30,083
[PROFESSOR] Hmm. I have
no idea what's happening

318
00:16:30,166 --> 00:16:32,750
on your end, gang, But it
looks like all those robots

319
00:16:32,833 --> 00:16:34,916
are converging on Main Street.

320
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:37,291
You guys should
probably check that out.

321
00:16:37,375 --> 00:16:38,750
On our way!

322
00:16:38,833 --> 00:16:40,500
