323
00:16:40,583 --> 00:16:43,541
Flying computers?
My phone can't do that!

324
00:16:46,833 --> 00:16:48,500
There's so many!
What are they doing?

325
00:16:48,583 --> 00:16:51,416
I don't know, but I don't
like the look of that swarm.

326
00:16:51,500 --> 00:16:54,291
[PC ROBOTS]
Fusion!

327
00:16:54,375 --> 00:16:56,416
What? Fusion?

328
00:17:02,625 --> 00:17:04,458
A giant PC?

329
00:17:06,375 --> 00:17:07,875
Look, it's her on the screen!

330
00:17:07,958 --> 00:17:09,625
[ARISA] That huge display
makes her wrinkles

331
00:17:09,708 --> 00:17:11,166
way more noticeable!

332
00:17:11,250 --> 00:17:13,375
If you're seeing this message,
that means I'm already dead,

333
00:17:13,458 --> 00:17:16,208
which I admit is a downer but at
least I can have the last word!

334
00:17:16,291 --> 00:17:19,000
Now that my beautiful dream
of conquering Akiba is in ruins,

335
00:17:19,083 --> 00:17:21,791
I'm going to take this
whole city down with me!

336
00:17:21,875 --> 00:17:24,500
Like hell you will!

337
00:17:24,583 --> 00:17:27,333
[GIANT PC roars]

338
00:17:27,416 --> 00:17:28,833
[PYUKO]
Ah...

339
00:17:28,916 --> 00:17:31,541
[GIANT PC roars]

340
00:17:31,625 --> 00:17:33,750
Moi! We have to stop this thing!

341
00:17:33,833 --> 00:17:36,708
[ARISA shouts]

342
00:17:36,791 --> 00:17:38,791
[GIANT PC shouts

343
