345
00:17:44,958 --> 00:17:49,916
[grunts]

346
00:17:52,291 --> 00:17:54,500
[ARISA groans]
It's just too strong!

347
00:17:54,583 --> 00:17:56,958
[ARISA screams]

348
00:17:57,041 --> 00:17:58,500
Arisa!

349
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:02,750
[MATOME screams]

