353
00:18:19,791 --> 00:18:21,958
Oh, no! I'm next
on the stomp list!

354
00:18:24,833 --> 00:18:25,958
[TAMOTSU]
Could that work?

355
00:18:26,041 --> 00:18:27,833
[GIANT PC
Die!

356
00:18:28,958 --> 00:18:30,500
[TAMOTSU]
