372
00:19:06,125 --> 00:19:09,375
Damn it! They can't
take Akiba away!

373
00:19:09,458 --> 00:19:11,041
It's the greatest
place on the planet!

374
00:19:11,125 --> 00:19:14,041
[gasps, grunts]

375
00:19:15,333 --> 00:19:17,375
[TAMOTSU gasps]

376
00:19:17,458 --> 00:19:19,041
[TAMOTSU]
What? Pyuko?

377
00:19:19,125 --> 00:19:22,000
[PYUKO]
Maximum speed engaged!

378
00:19:22,083 --> 00:19:24,333
[TAMOTSU]
