380
00:19:27,125 --> 00:19:33,000
[FEMALE PC VOICE]
25, 24, 23, 22, 21, 20...

381
00:19:33,083 --> 00:19:35,125
No! But you'll die! Come back!

382
00:19:35,208 --> 00:19:39,708
[FEMALE PC VOICE]
17, 16, 15, 14...

383
00:19:43,416 --> 00:19:47,166
Akiba precious.
