384
00:19:47,250 --> 00:19:50,625
[FEMALE PC VOICE]
5, 4. 3...

385
00:19:55,666 --> 00:19:58,250
[TAMOTSU gasps]

386
00:19:58,333 --> 00:20:02,000
Pyuko!

387
00:20:14,125 --> 00:20:17,291
We've been wondering
