393
00:20:29,708 --> 00:20:32,791
[TAMOTSU grunts] If that's true.
Then she went against her code!

394
00:20:32,875 --> 00:20:35,166
Yes, it seems like
a contradiction, but it's not.

395
00:20:35,250 --> 00:20:36,375
[TAMOTSU gasps]

396
00:20:36,458 --> 00:20:39,083
Think of Akihabara.
It has a long history.

397
00:20:39,166 --> 00:20:41,541
