in the last century.

398
00:20:41,625 --> 00:20:45,208
A black market in the burned
out city. An electronics hub.

399
00:20:45,291 --> 00:20:47,583
And now a home for otaku.

400
00:20:47,666 --> 00:20:49,333
Countless people's
memories and feelings

401
00:20:49,416 --> 00:20:50,916
are tied to these streets.

402
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:54,166
